94 /*========== Test Cases =====================================================*/
95 void testDIAG_AlertFlag(void) {
96  /* reset event sets the interlock back in ok mode */
97  DIAG_AlertFlag(DIAG_ID_ALERT_MODE, DIAG_EVENT_RESET, &diag_kpkDatabaseShim, 0u);
98  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(false, diag_kpkDatabaseShim.pTableError->alertFlagSetError);
99  /* ok event must not change the interlock state */
100  DIAG_AlertFlag(DIAG_ID_ALERT_MODE, DIAG_EVENT_OK, &diag_kpkDatabaseShim, 0u);
101  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(false, diag_kpkDatabaseShim.pTableError->alertFlagSetError);
102 
103  /* not ok event sets the alert mode back in not ok mode */
104  DIAG_AlertFlag(DIAG_ID_ALERT_MODE, DIAG_EVENT_NOT_OK, &diag_kpkDatabaseShim, 0u);
105  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(true, diag_kpkDatabaseShim.pTableError->alertFlagSetError);
106  /* Alert mode can not be reset via ok event, therefore the alert mode is still activated */
107  DIAG_AlertFlag(DIAG_ID_ALERT_MODE, DIAG_EVENT_OK, &diag_kpkDatabaseShim, 0u);
108  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(true, diag_kpkDatabaseShim.pTableError->alertFlagSetError);
109 
110  /* reset event sets the interlock back in ok mode */
111  DIAG_AlertFlag(DIAG_ID_ALERT_MODE, DIAG_EVENT_RESET, &diag_kpkDatabaseShim, 0u);
112  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(false, diag_kpkDatabaseShim.pTableError->alertFlagSetError);
113 }
114 
115 /** tests invalid input values */
116 void testDIAG_AlertFlagInvalidInput(void) {
117  TEST_ASSERT_FAIL_ASSERT(DIAG_AlertFlag(DIAG_ID_MAX, DIAG_EVENT_OK, &diag_kpkDatabaseShim, 0u));
118  TEST_ASSERT_FAIL_ASSERT(DIAG_AlertFlag(DIAG_ID_ALERT_MODE, 42, &diag_kpkDatabaseShim, 0u));
119  TEST_ASSERT_FAIL_ASSERT(DIAG_AlertFlag(DIAG_ID_ALERT_MODE, DIAG_EVENT_OK, NULL_PTR, 0u));
120 }
